     </p>

     <p class="container mt-3 position-absolute bottom-0 start-5">
          <strong>To sign in to your HabitSense account, simply follow these steps:</strong> <br /><br />

          <strong>1. &nbsp;</strong>Open the HabitSense app on your device. <br />
          <strong>2. &nbsp;</strong>Tap on the "Sign In" button to proceed. <br />
          <strong>3. &nbsp;</strong>Enter your registered email address or use your preferred social media account to
          log in quickly and securely.
          <br />
          <strong>4. &nbsp;</strong>Provide your password to authenticate your account and ensure the privacy of your
          data. <br />
          <strong>5. &nbsp;</strong>If you've forgotten your password, don't worry! Just click on the "Forgot Password"
